item.title: Planetside 2
item.dc:creator: TheeGoatPig
item.description:
Wow…I was playing the game back then and I never heard about this. Teamkilling a funeral? Wow…

Can’t wait for Planetside 2. The first game kept my interest for years. I have high hopes for what I have seen of the sequel. It should be lots of fun if the player base can get the numbers up.

Prox12 for the win.
